sequenceDiagram
    actor Human
    participant WebUI
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant GitHub
    participant Sync as Repo Sync Service
    participant Project as Project Service
    participant DB

    Human->>WebUI: Login with GitHub
    WebUI->>Auth: Start OAuth flow
    Auth->>GitHub: Redirect / authorize
    GitHub-->>Auth: OAuth callback with code
    Auth->>GitHub: Exchange code for token
    GitHub-->>Auth: Access token + user/org data
    Auth->>DB: Create/update user
    Auth->>Sync: Trigger initial repo/org sync
    Sync->>GitHub: Fetch orgs/repos
    GitHub-->>Sync: Repo list
    Sync->>Project: Provision/update projects
    Project->>DB: Save projects
    Auth-->>WebUI: Authenticated session
    WebUI-->>Human: Dashboard with synced projects
